{"tid":471536,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦：香港人是時候認識中共的自由了　","createTime":"2017-11-17T10:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T14:01:57.000Z","uid":141461,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0c0fb4546289bf5745d6d513bf65b4c8f87d0e86","tid":471536,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/n46058^s63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fn46058%5Es63.jpg&h=d33b1ad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】中聯辦法律部長王振民在一個研討會上，批評香港仍有人攻擊中國共產黨，糾纏於歷史上中共的不幸事件，是花崗岩頭腦，指港人是時候改變偏見。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦法律部長王振民在一個基本法研討會中指，國家憲法穩定，體制在國際上取得認可及支持，但偏偏在香港仍有人攻擊謾罵中國共產黨。他不認同有人指中共政權可怕、沒有自由，反問如果共產黨可怕，怎會成會最大外資投資國家？如果言論自由，怎會會有阿里巴巴和騰訊？呼籲港人是時候改變偏見。"},{"pid":"ab52e27aad7bfe99f3cc5b40b812406187382802","tid":471536,"uid":10905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:53:20.000Z","msg":"上到fb whatsapp先講野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b678ee02f9ad376828e731566c824344e3b185","tid":471536,"uid":31637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:54:07.000Z","msg":"中國特色言論自由"},{"pid":"55981f5907e76c4e4a78f4356cbeb76cccacebd1","tid":471536,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:55:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68bff11770ea70e565be23a78dca18120e6cf313","tid":471536,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:56:30.000Z","msg":"有讚美中國嘅自由"},{"pid":"52c6526c81692765d8917555afa726952d92dfcf","tid":471536,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底邊個先係花柳岩腦"},{"pid":"0d5c6d1ae0dbc24c225c0a5fd5aa7e17c68c8589","tid":471536,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:58:01.000Z","msg":"冇香港